ration becomes significant,\nthe imbibition rate decreases. The model predictions are compared with\nexperimental data for imbibition of water-ethanol mixtures into nanofiber mat\ncoatings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Mar 2020 18:29:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-22"}
