eir properties\nexperimentally can provide insights into the details of skyrmionic spin\nstructures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Mar 2020 14:45:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Aug 2020 15:05:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-18"}
